    "shortDesc": "Blindness\nWhat is Blindness?\nBlindness refers to the inability to perceive light or see, in varying degrees. In its most extreme\nform, it means the total absence of vision, where even light cannot be detected. This condition",
    "seoTitle": "Blindness - Causes, Symptoms, Diagnosis & Treatment | Ashu Laser Vision Mumbai",
    "seoDescription": "Learn about Blindness: causes, symptoms, diagnosis, treatment, prevention & FAQs. Expert eye care by Dr. Shahnawaz Kazi at Ashu Laser Vision, Andheri Mumbai - Super Specialty Eye Hospital since 2004. Book consultation.",
