    "seoDescription": "Learn about Thyroid Disorders: causes, symptoms, diagnosis, treatment, prevention & FAQs. Expert eye care by Dr. Shahnawaz Kazi at Ashu Laser Vision, Andheri Mumbai - Super Specialty Eye Hospital since 2004. Book consultation.",
