    "shortDesc": "Anti-VEGF Treatment\nAnti-VEGF (anti–vascular endothelial growth factor) treatment is a groundbreaking therapy used\nto manage and treat diseases that involve abnormal blood vessel growth in the eye. VEGF is\na protein that promotes the formation of new blood vessels. However, in ce",
