    "shortDesc": "Macular Hole\nA macular hole is a small break or opening in the macula, the central area of the retina\nresponsible for sharp, detailed central vision. The macula enables you to read, recognize faces,\ndrive, and perform tasks that require fine visual detail. When a hole forms, it c",
    "seoTitle": "Macular Hole - Causes, Symptoms, Diagnosis & Treatment | Ashu Laser Vision Mumbai",
    "seoDescription": "Learn about Macular Hole: causes, symptoms, diagnosis, treatment, prevention & FAQs. Expert eye care by Dr. Shahnawaz Kazi at Ashu Laser Vision, Andheri Mumbai - Super Specialty Eye Hospital since 2004. Book consultation.",
