    "shortDesc": "USG - B Scan\nUSG - B Scan, or B-scan ultrasonography, is a non-invasive diagnostic imaging technique used\nprimarily in ophthalmology to visualize the interior structures of the eye. It uses high-frequency\nsound waves to produce two-dimensional cross-sectional images, allowing det",
